text: Compsosoma geayi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gounelle in 1908. It is known from Brazil and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma geayi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1908
title: Compsosoma geayi
